text.tspan: Male deaths aged 90 to 99 years, 1950 to 2023
Number of deaths recorded annually, based on the civil calendar year, spanning from January 1 to December
31. This only includes males aged 90-99. Projections from 2024 onwards are based on the UN's low scenario.
Data source: UN, World Population Prospects (2024)
